        <![CDATA[
            Inspired by the warm hues and rustic feel of the autumn, this light theme aims to evoke a sense of
            comfort and tranquility. It blends soothing earth tones and crisp air-like whites, capturing the essence of
            fall leaves and late afternoon sunlight. The palette is designed to be gentle on the eyes, promoting focus
            and productivity.
